**The line that remembers the name:**

Line 6: `const username = ref('')`

This is the "sticky note" 📮 — it holds onto whatever you type in the input box. The `ref('')` part creates a reactive variable that Vue watches, so whenever you type something in the input box (via `v-model="username"`), it automatically updates this variable and remembers it for you.

